dcterms:description: A dataset of utility vectors for a food resource allocation task, involving various stakeholders such as donors, volunteers, dispatchers, and recipient organizations. The dataset includes utility functions learned from features like travel time, organization size, food access levels, and socio-economic factors.
dcterms:title: Utility vectors for food resource allocation task
